{"tid":873032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選管會簡介會   梁天琦：馮驊我屌你老母","createTime":"2018-10-23T06:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T14:57:36.000Z","uid":47359,"like":401,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"66de296007242165e7dcb3b0c0503d686c3e4ad8","tid":873032,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:49:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ajj4DH02Ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4ajj4DH02Ac&d=eZhh%2FlkBQm7FVMHtmBahcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d8650de8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ajj4DH02Ac</a><br />\n<br />\n【睇片】選管會簡介會　梁天琦：馮驊，食屎喇你<br />\n2016/8/2 &mdash; 20:02<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E9%81%B8%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B%E6%9C%83-%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6-%E9%A6%AE%E9%A9%8A-%E9%A3%9F%E5%B1%8E%E5%96%87%E4%BD%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6-%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25B1%258E%25E5%2596%2587%25E4%25BD%25A0%2F&d=eZhh%2FlkBQm7FVMHtmBahcjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2c5ea77f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E4%25BB%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6-%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25B1%258E%25E5%2596%2587%25E4%25BD%25A0%2F&h=55154aa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-%E9%81%B8%E7%AE%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%B0%A1%E4%BB%8B%E6%9C%83-%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6-%E9%A6%AE%E9%A9%8A-%E9%A3%9F%E5%B1%8E%E5%96%87%E4%BD%A0/</a><br />\n<br />\n選管會晚上7點在九龍灣國際展貿中心，為立法會候選人舉行簡介會，多名獲選管會通知已確認參選資格的候選人及其助選團陸續到場，將會為各候選人進行抽籤，決定其名單選舉編號。選舉管理委員會主席馮驊發言時，一度有泛民參選人走到台前叫口號，被裁定參選提名無效的本土民主前線梁天琦站在椅上高叫，「馮驊，食屎啦你！屌你老母！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n職員隨即要求保持安靜，注意用辭。在場也有人以粗口辱罵馮驊。在場則有人大力拍掌叫喊以示支持梁天琦，梁其後離開會場，稱再聽下去已無意思。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊開始發言時，一批泛民參選人走到台前高叫「反對政治篩選，維護公平選舉」等口號，抗議選管會阻止部份參選人出選，一度令簡介會暫停。"},{"pid":"8b80e3f8f924f0038c21f6e1a20dc141b2ee964f","tid":873032,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7027b4e0bff0dea7447fe1db2df1d03b3b15ef","tid":873032,"uid":36432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfdf15ada6d735fb48f9ed7288daead86c6dca1","tid":873032,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":170,"score":-158,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"佢而家去左邊？"},{"pid":"5801aaf0162de843f72d8c048af2511dddaee87e","tid":873032,"uid":47359,"like":199,"dislike":10,"score":189,"quote":{"pid":"ebfdf15ada6d735fb48f9ed7288daead86c6dca1","tid":873032,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":170,"score":-158,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"佢而家去左邊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:54:45.000Z","msg":"走啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"ca2ad1e11d043400032a1b375b7e80c58dea9c4a","tid":873032,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":88,"score":-87,"quote":{"pid":"ebfdf15ada6d735fb48f9ed7288daead86c6dca1","tid":873032,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":170,"score":-158,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"佢而家去左邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"梁天琦坐牢瘋狂慶祝區👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻🤟🏻<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bjeQBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bjeQBS</a>"},{"pid":"e7b966492074a48691c5f6e7915daa1dede36e2d","tid":873032,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht